Excel-Table3.t - test harness for Excel::Table object.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

perl Excel-Table3.t
[-h, --help]
[-m, --manual]

=head1 OPTIONS

=over 8

=item B<--help>

Prints a brief help message and exits.

